name: ssneld
params: class c0, class c1, class c2, wff w0

body.origin:
|- wi(w0, wi(wn(wcel(c0, c1)), wn(wcel(c0, c2))))
-| wi(w0, wi(wcel(c0, c2), wcel(c0, c1)))

cumulated.origin:
|- wi(w0, wi(wn(wcel(c0, c1)), wn(wcel(c0, c2))))
-| wi(w0, wi(wcel(c0, c2), wcel(c0, c1)))

body.origin:
|- wi(w0, wi(wcel(c0, c2), wcel(c0, c1)))
-| wi(w0, wss(c2, c1))

cumulated.origin:
|- wi(w0, wi(wn(wcel(c0, c1)), wn(wcel(c0, c2))))
-| wi(w0, wss(c2, c1))

comment: If a class is not in another class, it is also not in a subclass of that class. Deduction form. (Contributed by David Moews, 1-May-2017.)
